name: Cube Stacking Rings
description:
These 3 rings work together to create a stack of cubes in marble and grey tones. Each handmade cube is placed upon an adjustable brass ring. They can be worn together or on their own.

Each item is handmade by myself and must be worn with care as would any item of jewellery.

name: Marble Brass Necklace
description:
This elegant necklace consists of 3 handmade beads in marble and concrete grey and 2 vintage cut brass tube beads. Its made up onto a 32" gold plated chain, and is fitted with a gold plated lobster clasp.

Each item is handmade by myself, so yours may differ slightly from picture, that's what makes it unique!

Please treat each item with care as you would any jewellery.

Thanks xo
